Type of Feat: Class
Prerequisite: Barbarian.
Specifics: The barbarian may rage and the effects are determined by which style of rage they took at 1st level, standard or whirlwind frenzy.
Use: Selected. The barbarian may use this ability once per day at first level, +1 use per day at level 4, and every 4 levels thereafter.  The feat has a cooldown timer that lasts as long as the length of the rage and fatigue (if any). This is an instantly activated feat.